      <![CDATA[<h2 id="「ZZZ-2-7」炎炙沸釜-击破-（★★★★）"><a href="#「ZZZ-2-7」炎炙沸釜-击破-（★★★★）" class="headerlink" title="「ZZZ 2.7」炎炙沸釜[击破]（★★★★）"></a>「ZZZ 2.7」炎炙沸釜[击破]（★★★★）</h2><img onerror="imgOnError(this);" data-fancybox="gallery" src="/images/绝区零/引擎/炎炙沸釜[击破]（★★★★）.jpg" width="200" alt="图片" data-caption="图片" loading="lazy">冲击力 15%红油辣锅发动[支援突击] 时，装备者对目标造成的失衡值提升7.2/8.2/9.2/10.2/11.5%，装备者造成的伤害提升7.2/8.2/9.2/10.2/11.5%，持续30秒，重复触发时刷新持续时间。<p>The Simmering Pot[Stun]（★★★★）<br>Impact 15%<br>When activating an Assist<br>Follow-Up, the equipper’s Daze inflicted on the target increases by 7.2&#x2F;8.2&#x2F;9.2&#x2F;10.2&#x2F;11.5%, and DMG dealt increases by 7.2&#x2F;8.2&#x2F;9.2&#x2F;10.2&#x2F;11.5%<br> for 30s. Repeated triggers reset the duration.</p>]]>
