      <![CDATA[<hr><p>「HI3rd 8.8」<br>第二部新箱庭地图<br>地丰·曙影区</p><hr><p>新头像框<br><img onerror="imgOnError(this);" data-fancybox="gallery" src="/images/崩坏三/头像框/1.jpg" width="200" alt="图片" data-caption="图片" loading="lazy"><br>「HI3rd 8.8」<br>V1已发包，版本号为8.8.12</p><hr><p>「HI3rd 8.8」<br>当芽衣使用游云作为协同者并开启星之环时，有特殊语音</p><hr><p>「HI3rd」<br>关于8.9：<br>正如Dim之前所述，8.9的S级女武神装甲是希儿。<br>希儿使用两种武器作战，分别是使用镰刀（Scythe）进行近战爆发输出和使用法杖（Staff）进行远程攻击。她的属性可能是火。星环特性可能包含复盈相生。<br>STC</p><p>Regarding 8.9:<br>As Dim previously stated, the 8.9 S is Seele.<br>Seele uses two types of weapons in combat, namely the Scythe for melee burst output and the Staff for ranged attacks. Her attribute may be fire.<br>The characteristics of star rings may include energy.<br>STC</p>]]>
